if you want more
detail or suggestions

00:03:09.380 --> 00:03:11.350
on how to use the API.

00:03:11.350 --> 00:03:13.780
Those steps will get you started
on using the Player Stats

00:03:13.780 --> 00:03:17.330
API so you can refine your
game and target those responses

00:03:17.330 --> 00:03:20.320
to players individually,
make them happier,

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:22.490
and make your games
more profitable.

00:03:22.490 --> 00:03:25.040
So have fun, and let
us know in comments

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:26.540
if you have any new
ways that you've

00:03:26.540 --> 00:03:29.450
thought of using the stats
to make your games better.

